Welcome to the Navi-Tour App.  This app is used to host and explore local tours via your iOS app, the Denso NaviBridge App and your Denso GPS unit.  

This app was developed using Titanium Alloy, Appcelerator Cloud Services, NaviBridge Module, and the Google Places API.

Use the App to explore either tours or destinations, add your own tour and then add great destinations to share day tours with friends and other users.

To Use:

-Download Code
-Download the Denso NaviBride Module
-Build App on Titanium Alloy using 2.1.3GA SDK